w-wrap: break-word;"><span style=3D"font-size: 16px;"><strong>Main Revision=
s</strong></span></p>
<div style=3D"word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word;">
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">=E2=80=A2 I=
ntroduced the Loyalties Policy</p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">- In conjun=
ction with the previously announced overhaul of our Loyalties System, a new=
 Loyalties Policy has been added to our Operational Policies. This policy o=
utlines the terms for earning, using, expiring, and the limitations on Loya=
lties. Detailed guidance regarding these provisions will be provided in lin=
e with the Loyalties System overhaul schedule.</p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">=E2=80=A2 R=
evised the "Item" and "Fairy" Categories in the Recovery Support Criteria</=
p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">The recover=
y support criteria have been updated to reflect the volume of recovery requ=
ests received via our Support, including the exclusion of certain recovery =
services.</p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style=3D"word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;">We hope you=
 review the updated recovery support items and that these changes will not =
cause any inconvenience in your use of our services. We remain fully commit=
ted to improving your gaming experience.</p>
